Scott: Well, mostly because of recording.

20
00:01:12,943 --> 00:01:14,159
Scott: If you don't want to record, it's fine.

21
00:01:14,940 --> 00:01:18,540
Rym: Yeah, but if you want to record, even on a good PC, you need two computers, basically.

22
00:01:19,020 --> 00:01:19,205
Scott: Yeah.

23
